description: Details of Phase one of redevelopment of site involving demolition of existing buildings and provision of 112 dwellings (55 affordable units) in a range of two to six storey buildings comprising thirty nine 1 bedroomed and fifty eight 2 bedroomed self contained flats, one 4 bedroomed, four 2 bedroomed, and ten 3 bedroomed terraced houses together with a new community centre, retail shop and enhancement to riverside walk. Provision of refuse stores, 112 cycle spaces, 132 car parking spaces, new access roads and cycle routes. (Approval of reserved matters application to determine appearance landscaping and scale pursuant to condition 7 of outline approval ref: C2006/56803/OUT).
